        {
            "title": "美股道指跌142點　納指再破頂一周升1.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股個別發展，納指再創收市新高。市場繼續關注美國關稅政策的最新發展及企業業績。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230831_FI_source-ap_美股3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230831_FI_source-ap_美股3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯指數收報44342點，跌142點，跌幅0.32%。高開87點後隨即轉跌，最多下滑259點，低見44224點。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230831_FI_source-ap_美股3.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230831_FI_source-ap_美股3.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/07/Earns_Tesla_42500_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/07/Earns_Tesla_42500_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230831_FI_source-ap_美股3.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/07/Earns_Tesla_42500_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數報20895點，升10點，升幅0.05%，曾高見20980點，升幅達到0.45%，其後最多轉挫0.19%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數報6296點，跌不足1點，一度高見6315點，上漲0.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，納指升1.5%，標普500指數升0.59%，道指下跌 0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Travelers升1.6%，為表現最強道指成份股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">3M跌3.6%，為表現最差道指成份股，公司業績好過預期，但表示關稅的影響將主要在下半年反映。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Netflix上季收入好過預期，但未能達到最樂觀的市場預測，股價挫5.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/724x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">亞馬遜裁減雲端運算部門職位，有報道指涉數以百計職位，股價反覆回升1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">特斯拉(Tesla)反彈3.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大型油企雪佛龍(Chevron)在仲裁中獲勝，並已完成收購頁岩油商Hess，刺激雪佛龍股價一度上揚3%，收市倒跌0.9%；Hess則漲6.8%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/07/Earns_Tesla_42500_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/07/Earns_Tesla_42500_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15103031-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c142%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%80%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e5%86%8d%e7%a0%b4%e9%a0%82%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%8d%871-5",
